      "role": "user",
      "content": "everything is gone. the company, the funding, the house... i lost it all in the crash. i cant even look my parents in the eye. the debt is so high i dont see a way back. i just feel like a total failure and the shame is actually physically painful. i dont think i can keep going like this.",
